<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8"/>
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0"/>
  <title>{{days_remaining}} Days Until Your Exam!</title>
  <style>
    body { margin:0; padding:0; background:#f4f6f9; font-family:'Segoe UI', Arial, sans-serif; color:#333; }
    .container { max-width:560px; margin:40px auto; background:#ffffff; border-radius:12px; overflow:hidden; box-shadow:0 4px 24px rgba(0,0,0,0.08); }
    .header { background:linear-gradient(135deg, #7c3aed 0%, #4f46e5 100%); padding:32px 40px; text-align:center; }
    .countdown { font-size:72px; font-weight:900; color:#ffffff; line-height:1; display:block; }
    .days-label { font-size:16px; color:rgba(255,255,255,0.8); margin-top:4px; }
    .body { padding:36px 40px; }
    .exam-info { background:#f5f3ff; border-left:4px solid #7c3aed; padding:14px 18px; border-radius:6px; margin-bottom:20px; }
    .cta a { display:inline-block; background:#7c3aed; color:#fff; text-decoration:none; padding:16px 40px; border-radius:10px; font-size:16px; font-weight:700; }
    .footer { background:#f4f6f9; padding:20px 40px; text-align:center; font-size:12px; color:#9ca3af; }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="header">
      <span class="countdown">{{days_remaining}}</span>
      <div class="days-label">day{{#if (gt days_remaining 1)}}s{{/if}} until your exam ⚡</div>
    </div>
    <div class="body">
      <p>Hi <strong>{{user_name}}</strong>,</p>
      <p>Your <strong>{{subject}}</strong> exam is coming up fast. Now is the time to intensify your preparation.</p>

      <div class="exam-info">
        📅 <strong>Exam Date:</strong> {{exam_date}}<br/>
        📚 <strong>Subject:</strong> {{subject}}
      </div>

      <p>Practice past questions regularly in the final stretch — it's the most effective way to consolidate what you've learned.</p>

      <div style="text-align:center; margin:24px 0;">
        <a href="{{quiz_link}}">Start a Practice Session →</a>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="footer">&copy; {{year}} {{institution_name}} &middot; Powered by FuhsoX</div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
